Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.84,0:23:55.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...saying there's a dead body in the forest in front of the mansion!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.67,0:23:57.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?!
