Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.65,0:24:08.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh? How pathetic does a guy have to be to work under {\i1}that{\i0} dimwit?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.33,0:24:14.34,Dialogue,,10,10,0,,On the next Conan: 'Heiji Hattori and the Vampire Mansion (Three)'!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.34,0:24:19.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Next Conan's Hint: Stake!
